quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  17,101,"Gom…óii Men okkiino Muusaa Aayeeje jeenay …ìanngu…óe, lanndii …ìi…ì…ìe Israa'iila …ìen tuma nde o arunoo …ìe Fir'awna wi'ani mo: \"Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Muusaa ko a mbil…óaa…óo"
  17,102,"Maaku: \"Go…óii hi…óa anndi jippinaali …óee si wanaa Jey…óo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin Aayeeje [yi'etee…ói]. Min dey mi…óo sikkumaa ko an yo Fir'awna ko a halkii…óo"
  17,103,O faalaa nde o dillinta …ìe ka leydi Men yooli mo e …ìen wonndu…ìe e makko …ìe denndaangal
  17,104,"Men Daalani …ìaawo makko …ìi…ì…ìe Israa'iila …ìen: \"Ho…óee ka leydi, si fodoore sakkitiinde nden arii, Men adday on ko on muu…ìii…ìe=fiiliibe"
  17,105,"Ko sabu Goonga Men telliniri nde, ko sabu Goonga nde tellii, Men nuliraali ma si wanaa [ko a] wewlinoowo=beltinoowo e jertinoowo"
  17,106,"E Qur'aanaare Men …ìanngini nde fii yo a janngannde yim…ìe …ìen e dow dee∆¥ere, Men jippini nde jipinnde"
  17,107,"Maaku: \"Gom…óinee nde, maa…óun wata on gom…óin, pellet, …ìen okkaa…ìe ganndal ko adii nde si [nde] janngaama e taweende ma…ì…ìe …ìe suuyiray wokku…óe ko …ìe sujjoo…ìe"
  17,108,"∆Åe wi'a:Senaade woodanii Joomi amen,nde wonnoo Fodoore Joomi amen nden ko wa…óoore"
  17,109,"Hi…ìe suuyira wokku…óe …ìe wulla [Alqur'aana on] …ìayda …ìe yankinaare"
  17,110,"Maaku: \"Noddiree Mo Alla maa noddiro Mo Hinnorante, kala no noddir…óon Mo, ko Kanko In…óe Mo∆¥∆¥e …óen heeranii, wata a fen√±in julde maa…óa nden wata a suudu nde …óa…ì…ìu hakkunde …óun laawol"
  17,111,"Maaku: Yettoore nden woodanii Alla On Mo jogitaaki …ìi…ó…óo laatanaaki Mo kafidaa…óo e Laamu laatanaaki Mo teddu…óo mo O huykinantoo, Mawnin Mo Mawninndee"